# .gitignore (模板版)
# 复制到新项目后，将自动保护归档元数据不被误上传

# 1. 归档元数据
manifest.yaml
archive_gen.py
deploy.sh
Project_Summary.md
Archive_Log.md

# 2. 知识库目录
_Archive/
_Notebook/

# 3. 系统垃圾与临时文件
node_modules/
.env
*.log
*.tmp
__pycache__/
*:Zone.Identifier
.DS_Store
Xserver_G_Multi_Renew_Project_Summary.md
Xserver_G_Multi_Renew_Archive_Log.md
Xserver_G_Multi_Renew_Project_Supplements.md

# 4. 续期状态（含账号信息，不应公开）
status.json
